'''Tiyizim''', ina di fiil a [[Rilijan|komparitiv rilijan]], a di [[biliif]] ina di egzistans a [[diyiti]].<ref>
[http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/theism/ theism, n.], Merriam-Webster Online Dictionary, axes 2011-03-18 </ref> Ina papila paalans, di term ''tiyizim'' muotaim diskraib di klasikal kansepshan a gad (ar nof gad) we fain ina di [[Monotiyizim|monotiyistik]] ah [[Palitiyizim|palitiyistik]] rilijan.

Di toerm ''tiyizim'' diraiv frah di Griik ''theos'' miinin "gad". Di toerm ''tiyizim'' eh fos yuuz bai Ralf Kodwot (Ralph Cudworth, 1617–1688).<ref>Halsey, William, Robert H. Blackburn and Sir Frank Francis, ''Collier's Encyclopedia'', ed. Louis Shores, Crowell-Collier Educational Corporation, 1969, 20th edition, Vol. 22, pp. 266–7</ref> Ina fi Kodwot definishan, deh "schrikli ah prapali kaal Tiyis, uu afoerm, se wah poerfek kanchos andastandin biin, ar main, egzis a iself frah itoerniti, ena di kaaz a aal ada tingz".<ref>Cudworth, Ralph (1678). ''The True Intellectual System of the Universe, Vol. I''. New York: Gould & Newman, 1837, p. 267.</ref>

